column3: Concept ACK, agree that we should change the qt config to `-no-jpeg`, and also remove `libjpeg` from `doc/dependencies.md`

Added `-no-libjpeg` to Qts configure flags, and removed jpeg from `doc/dependencies.md`. \nAlso added a commit that removes the line numbers from the qt packages that we reference in there, as at the moment they are constantly incorrect.

<!--e57a25ab6845829454e8d69fc972939a-->

The following sections might be updated with supplementary metadata relevant to reviewers and maintainers.
